Nabban	<b>Disambiguation:</b><br>• <a href="bword://Nabban (duchy)">Nabban (duchy)</a> - Duchy on the central western coast of Osten Ard, one of the major human powers of the continent<br>• <a href="bword://Nabban (city)">Nabban (city)</a> - Capital and largest city of the Duchy of Nabban, chief urban center of Nabbanai power
